<A>__{there is a sudden scream! one of the villagers stumbles upon something. everyone gathers around the villager. a corpse lies before them. the body has a somewhat rubbery appearance, as if all of its bones had been broken. the man's pale, greenish face is frozen in a hideous grimace. indiana and macgowan stare in shock. the villagers whisper among themselves.}
