<B>__{an ancient scottish castle.}
<A>__{an enormous, 16th century stone structure. tall, forboding towers, lined with menacing gargoyles, pierce the night sky. the castle appears deserted. its interior is completely dark, save for a small, flickering candlelight. it burns from the castle's upstairs window. indiana gives a questioning look to macgowan. the inpector points to the castle's upstairs window.}
<C>__{macgowan}
